Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: 1125 Seventeenth Street is conveniently located in the Central Business District at 17th and Lawrence Street, with direct access to I-25 via Auraria parkway to the south and 20th Street to the north. 1125 17th Street is one block north of 16th Street Mall, within walking distance of Lower Downtown, fine dining, upscale hotels, athletic clubs, Coors Field and the Denver Center for Performing Arts.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
1125 17th Street is a 25-story Class A building offering spectacular panoramic mountain views and features amenities such as banking facilities, on-site management and 24-hour security, as well as immediate access to Skyline Park and the Westin Hotel.

Winner of the 1998 BOMA Building of the Year Award for buildings over 500,000 SF, this property offers 24-hour security and a location adjacent to Skyline Park and the Westin Hotel. 1735 Lawrence St. (Bldg B) is a separate building, but is connected to this property. 1125 17th St. has a separate identity and its own entrance.
